---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Siddhesh Lakhani"
  description="Full Stack Engineer from Mumbai — Linux enthusiast, Next.js developer, freelance builder."
  activePage="about"
>
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="grid-bg"></div>
      <div class="about-hero-inner">
        <div class="section-tag">My Story</div>
        <h1 class="section-h">
          Know me<br /><span style="color:var(--red)">Better.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="section-sub">
          Full Stack Engineer | Linux · FOSS | Freelance Developer | Building
          production-grade systems
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-section">
      <div class="bio-text">
        <p>
          I'm <strong>Siddhesh Lakhani</strong>, a Full Stack Developer based in
          Mumbai. I specialize in building production-grade systems using <strong
            >Next.js, Express, PostgreSQL, and Docker</strong
          >. My workflow is driven by a deep interest in <strong
            >Arch Linux</strong
          > and systems programming, running a custom-patched <strong
            >DWM</strong
          > setup to keep things lightweight and efficient.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe in <strong>minimalism</strong>, both in design and
          functionality. This means shipping fast, owning my stack, and ensuring
          that every line of code serves a purpose. Whether it's debugging
          low-level kernel interactions or fine-tuning a pixel-perfect UI, I
          focus on performance and control.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently, I'm deep-diving into <strong>Linux kernel internals</strong
          > and exploring <strong>systems programming</strong> to understand the layers
          beneath the application. When I'm not at the terminal, you'll find me gaming,
          vibing to music, or pushing limits in sports.
        </p>
        <div class="bio-ctas">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Let's Build Together</a>
          <a href="/Resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-outline"
            >Download Resume ↗</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="values-list">
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="value-title">Ship Fast</div><div class="value-desc">
                Build MVPs, iterate quickly, optimize when needed. Don't
                over-engineer.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"
                ></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="value-title">Own Your Stack</div><div
                class="value-desc"
              >
                Self-host when possible. Control your data, your infra, your
                systems.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path
                  d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364-6.364l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707m12.728 0l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="value-title">Minimalism First</div><div
                class="value-desc"
              >
                Less noise, more signal — in code, in design, in tooling.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M4 17l6-6-6-6M12 19h8"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="value-title">Linux Purist</div><div
                class="value-desc"
              >
                Arch + DWM. Full control. No bloat. Riced and suckless.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon><polyline
                  points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline><polyline
                  points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline></svg
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="value-title">Full-Stack Thinking</div><div
                class="value-desc"
              >
                From DB schema to pixel-perfect UI — I think end-to-end.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stack-section">
      <div class="section-tag">My Stack</div>
      <h2 class="section-h" style="margin-bottom:4px;">
        Technologies I<br /><span style="color:var(--red)">Work With.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="stack-categories">
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Frontend</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Next.js</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >React</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">TypeScript</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >TailwindCSS</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">Astro</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Backend</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Express</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Node.js</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">Python</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Bun</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Databases</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">PostgreSQL</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >MySQL</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">Supabase</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Prisma</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">Firebase</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Infra</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Docker</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Nginx</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Cloudflare</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">Vercel</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ ML / CV</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">TensorFlow</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >PyTorch</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">OpenCV</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Keras</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">scikit-learn</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Systems</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Linux</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Rust</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">C++</span><span class="stack-pill"
              >Bash</span
            >
            <span class="stack-pill">Git</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="beyond-section">
      <div class="inner">
        <div class="section-tag" style="padding:0;">Beyond the Terminal</div>
        <h2 class="section-h" style="margin:12px 0 0;">
          Life outside<br /><span style="color:var(--red)">the code.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="beyond-grid">
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-header">
              <div class="beyond-icon">
                <svg
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><line x1="6" y1="12" x2="10" y2="12"></line><line
                    x1="8"
                    y1="10"
                    x2="8"
                    y2="14"></line><circle cx="15.5" cy="15.5" r=".5"
                  ></circle><circle cx="18.5" cy="12.5" r=".5"></circle><path
                    d="M18 5H6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h12a3 3 0 0 0 3-3V8a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
              </div>
              <div class="beyond-title">Gaming</div>
            </div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">
              Competitive gamer. Clutch plays and game-winning moments fuel the
              same energy as solving hard bugs.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-header">
              <div class="beyond-icon">
                <svg
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"></path><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"
                  ></circle><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"></circle></svg
                >
              </div>
              <div class="beyond-title">Music</div>
            </div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">
              Always vibing. Music is the background process running while I
              ship features.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-header">
              <div class="beyond-icon">
                <svg
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"></path><path
                    d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"></path><path d="M4 22h16"
                  ></path><path
                    d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"
                  ></path><path
                    d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"
                  ></path><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2z"></path></svg
                >
              </div>
              <div class="beyond-title">Sports</div>
            </div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">
              Pushing limits physically. Competition and performance — on the
              field and in the terminal.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-header">
              <div class="beyond-icon">
                <svg
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path
                    d="M5 18a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6zM19 18a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6zM9 17h6M13 12h-4L7 8h6l2 4zM14 12l2.5-3.5H20"
                  ></path></svg
                >
              </div>
              <div class="beyond-title">Biking</div>
            </div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">
              Riding my RE Meteor 350 through open landscapes. It’s where I find
              my best ideas and clearest focus.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-block">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <div class="section-tag" style="display:inline-block;margin-bottom:20px;">
        What's next?
      </div>
      <h2>
        Let's build<br /><span style="color:var(--red)">something great.</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        Open to freelance projects, technical discussions, and interesting
        collaborations. Don't be a stranger.
      </p>
      <div class="btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="btn-outline">See My Work</a>
        <a href="/Resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-outline">Resume ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ABOUT PAGE */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 120px 52px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-hero .grid-bg {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .about-hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .about-hero-inner .section-h {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .about-hero-inner .section-sub {
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  /* BIO SECTION */
  .bio-section {
    padding: 0 52px 80px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .bio-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .bio-text p strong {
    color: var(--off);
  }
  .bio-text .bio-ctas {
    margin-top: 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* VALUES */
  .values-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .value-item {
    background: var(--char2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .value-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--red-border);
  }
  .value-icon {
    color: var(--red);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .value-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--off);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .value-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* STACK SECTION */
  .stack-section {
    padding: 0 52px 80px;
  }
  .stack-categories {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .stack-cat {
    background: var(--char2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 24px 22px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .stack-cat:hover {
    border-color: var(--red-border);
  }
  .stack-cat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .stack-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 7px;
  }
  .stack-pill {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--off2);
    background: var(--char3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition:
      border-color 0.2s,
      color 0.2s;
  }
  .stack-pill:hover {
    border-color: var(--red);
    color: var(--off);
  }

  /* BEYOND CODE */
  .beyond-section {
    padding: 0 52px 96px;
    background: var(--char2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 0 0 80px;
  }
  .beyond-section .inner {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  .beyond-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .beyond-card {
    background: var(--char3);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .beyond-card:first-child {
    border-left: none;
  }
  .beyond-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    height: 24px; /* Fix height to ensure vertical baseline is consistent */
  }
  .beyond-icon {
    color: var(--red);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .beyond-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--off);
    line-height: normal;
  }
  .beyond-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA BLOCK */
  .cta-block {
    padding: 0 52px 96px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-block .glow {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 500px;
    height: 280px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(255, 59, 59, 0.08) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-block h2 {
    font-family: "Syne", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cta-block p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 420px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .cta-block .btns {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero,
    .bio-section,
    .stack-section,
    .cta-block,
    .terminal-wrap {
      padding-left: 20px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    }
    .bio-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .stack-categories {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .beyond-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .beyond-section {
      padding-left: 20px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
